Hello! Welcome to my web page. 
I am a post-doc researcher at [https://www.mirmi.tum.de/en/rsi/home/ RSI] at the Technical University of Munich. 
My main research topic is control theory and its applications in robotics systems. 

[https://scholar.google.com.br/citations?user=l2vA2wUAAAAJ \[Google Scholar\]]\n
[https://orcid.org/0000-0002-7336-1443 \[ORCid\]]\n
[https://www.researchgate.net/profile/Hugo_Kussaba \[ResearchGate\]]\n
[https://impactstory.org/u/0000-0002-7336-1443 \[Impactstory\]]\n
[http://publons.com/a/890823/ \[Plubons\]]\n
[https://github.com/htadashi \[GitHub\]]\n
[https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/User:Saung_Tadashi \[Wikipedia\]]\n
[http://lattes.cnpq.br/2586485528922581 \[CV Lattes\]]\n

= Research interests
- Hybrid dynamical systems.
- Control and estimation on Lie groups.
- Linear matrix inequalities
- Applications of real algebraic geometry on optimization.
- Finite time stability and boundedness.

= Other 
- An upper bound for my Erdős number is [https://www.csauthors.net/distance/paul-erdos/h-t-m-kussaba six].

